name: PSYOPCAT
description: Psyopcat is the Mascot Memecoin for Satspump.fun, an upcoming project aiming to decentralize the sats pump ecosystem. Built using the CAT20 protocol, the project emphasizes innovation on Bitcoin-compatible networks. Satspump.fun is designed to foster growth in the Bitcoin DeFi sector, offering tools for token creation, trading, and community engagement​ Psyopcat, as a memecoin, serves both a symbolic and practical role in the Satspump.fun ecosystem. It reflects the fun and engaging side of the platform while building a community around the project.
